SiteIndex.name: SiteIndex
SiteIndex.description: This textual convention defines a greater than zero value used to identify an external group operating autonomously from the local group.

SiteIndexOrZero.name: SiteIndexOrZero
SiteIndexOrZero.description: This textual convention is an extension of the SiteIndex convention. The latter defines a greater than zero value used to identify an external group operating autonomously from the local group. This extension permits the additional value of zero. the value zero is object-specific and must therefore be defined as part of the description of any object which uses this syntax. Examples of the usage of zero might include situations where the site is unknown or not relevant

Unsigned64.name: Unsigned64
Unsigned64.description: A non-negative 64-bit bit integer, without counter semantics.

PoolQuotaType.name: PoolQuotaType
PoolQuotaType.description: The format of the adminQuota value: 0 - Unlimited quota, 1 - Size in Megabytes.

StatusEnabledDefault.name: StatusEnabledDefault
StatusEnabledDefault.description: This textual convention can be used to define a status of enabled or disabled. The value 0 is assigned to enabled

eqlStoragePoolTable.name: eqlStoragePoolTable
eqlStoragePoolTable.description: EqualLogic-Persistent Storage Pool Table. This table contains a list of storage pools in a group and their attributes.

eqlStoragePoolEntry.name: eqlStoragePoolEntry
eqlStoragePoolEntry.description: An entry (row) containing storage pool info.

eqlStoragePoolIndex.name: eqlStoragePoolIndex
eqlStoragePoolIndex.description: This field specifies a unique index for identifying a storage pool.

eqlStoragePoolRowStatus.name: eqlStoragePoolRowStatus
eqlStoragePoolRowStatus.description: This field is used indicate the status of this entry.

eqlStoragePoolName.name: eqlStoragePoolName
eqlStoragePoolName.description: EQL-SECONDARY-KEY This field specifies a user friendly name for a storage pool. The name must be unique within a group. The name must not contain spaces or special characters. The name can be up to 64 characters in length.

eqlStoragePoolDefaultFlag.name: eqlStoragePoolDefaultFlag
eqlStoragePoolDefaultFlag.description: This field specifies if this storage pool is the default pool. TRUE == default pool.

eqlStoragePoolRAIDConfigWaitFlag.name: eqlStoragePoolRAIDConfigWaitFlag
eqlStoragePoolRAIDConfigWaitFlag.description: This field specifies if the system should wait for a configured RAID-set before allowing volumes to be created.

eqlStoragePoolShouldEvalMask.name: eqlStoragePoolShouldEvalMask
eqlStoragePoolShouldEvalMask.description: This field specifies one or more reasons (32-bit mask) the pool should be evaluated.

eqlStoragePoolLastBalance.name: eqlStoragePoolLastBalance
eqlStoragePoolLastBalance.description: This field specifies a timestamp of the last time the pool was balanced.

eqlStoragePoolDescription.name: eqlStoragePoolDescription
eqlStoragePoolDescription.description: This field contains a description of the storage pool.

eqlStoragePoolLeadMemberId.name: eqlStoragePoolLeadMemberId
eqlStoragePoolLeadMemberId.description: This field is deprecated and will be unsupported in the next release.

eqlStoragePoolUUID.name: eqlStoragePoolUUID
eqlStoragePoolUUID.description: EQL-SECONDARY-KEY This field is for internal use only.

eqlStoragePoolExecMergeTo.name: eqlStoragePoolExecMergeTo
eqlStoragePoolExecMergeTo.description: This field, when non-zero, specifies the index of the storage pool that this pool is being merged into.

eqlStoragePoolBorrow.name: eqlStoragePoolBorrow
eqlStoragePoolBorrow.description: This field specifies if borrowing is enabled for this pool.

eqlStoragePoolSnapTrimThreshold.name: eqlStoragePoolSnapTrimThreshold
eqlStoragePoolSnapTrimThreshold.description: This field specifies the threshold % of the pool capacity that indicates when to begin trimming.

eqlStoragePoolSnapTrimBuffer.name: eqlStoragePoolSnapTrimBuffer
eqlStoragePoolSnapTrimBuffer.description: This field specifies how far below the SnapTrimThreshold to trim in MB.

eqlStoragePoolSnapTrimmerHWMLifeTime.name: eqlStoragePoolSnapTrimmerHWMLifeTime
eqlStoragePoolSnapTrimmerHWMLifeTime.description: This field defines the amount of time (in secs) that the trimmer will use Volume In Use HWM to calculate the borrowed space for the thin volume. Default is 10 days

eqlStoragePoolSnapTrimmerBorrowInfoRefre.name: eqlStoragePoolSnapTrimmerBorrowInfoRefreshInterval
eqlStoragePoolSnapTrimmerBorrowInfoRefre.description: This field defines the amount of time (in secs) after which the snap trimmer will attempt to refresh its borrow information

eqlStoragePoolDefaultCompressionStrategy.name: eqlStoragePoolDefaultCompressionStrategy
eqlStoragePoolDefaultCompressionStrategy.description: Default value for how compression for snapshots should be set if not specified.

eqlStoragePoolDefaultCompressionMinSnapD.name: eqlStoragePoolDefaultCompressionMinSnapDelay
eqlStoragePoolDefaultCompressionMinSnapD.description: The value of this object represents how long to wait prior to marking a snapshot as eligible for automatic compression. Current default is 10 minutes.

eqlStoragePoolDefaultCompressionMinSnapA.name: eqlStoragePoolDefaultCompressionMinSnapAge
eqlStoragePoolDefaultCompressionMinSnapA.description: The value of this object represents the minimum amout of time a snapshot is expected to kept around in order to be marked for automatic compression. Current default is 23 hours.

eqlStoragePoolSnapMemberTrimThresholdAmo.name: eqlStoragePoolSnapMemberTrimThresholdAmount
eqlStoragePoolSnapMemberTrimThresholdAmo.description: This field specifies the per member trimming threshold used by the trimmer in MB. The default value of 204800 MB (200 GB) represents the minimum value for this field.

eqlStoragePoolSnapTrimRecheckTimer.name: eqlStoragePoolSnapTrimRecheckTimer
eqlStoragePoolSnapTrimRecheckTimer.description: This field defines the interval (in seconds) that will be used to determine if trimming needs to occur.

eqlStoragePoolStatsTable.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsTable
eqlStoragePoolStatsTable.description: EqualLogic-Dynamic Storage Pool Statistics Table. This table contains a list of pools in a group and their statistics.

eqlStoragePoolStatsEntry.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsEntry
eqlStoragePoolStatsEntry.description: An entry (row) containing storage pool stats.

eqlStoragePoolStatsSpace.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsSpace
eqlStoragePoolStatsSpace.description: This field specifies how many MB of space comprises this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsSpaceUsed.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsSpaceUsed
eqlStoragePoolStatsSpaceUsed.description: This field specifies the space used by volumes in this pool. The value is represented in MB. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsFreeSpace.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsFreeSpace
eqlStoragePoolStatsFreeSpace.description: This field specifies how many MB of space is available in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsReplicationSpace.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsReplicationSpace
eqlStoragePoolStatsReplicationSpace.description: This field specifies how many MB of space is allocated for replication in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsReplicationSpaceUsed.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsReplicationSpaceUsed
eqlStoragePoolStatsReplicationSpaceUsed.description: This field specifies how many MB of space is currently utilized by replication in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsReplicationFreeSpace.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsReplicationFreeSpace
eqlStoragePoolStatsReplicationFreeSpace.description: This field specifies how many MB of space is available to replication in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsMemberNumOnline.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsMemberNumOnline
eqlStoragePoolStatsMemberNumOnline.description: This field indicates how many members are online in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsMemberCount.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsMemberCount
eqlStoragePoolStatsMemberCount.description: This field indicates how many total members are in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotReserved.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotReserved
eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotReserved.description: This field specifies how many MB of snapshot space is reserved in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotUsed.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotUsed
eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotUsed.description: This field specifies how many MB of snapshot space is currently utilized in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotNumInUse.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotNumInUse
eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotNumInUse.description: This field indicates how many snapshots are currently in use in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotNumOnline.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotNumOnline
eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotNumOnline.description: This field indicates how many snapshots are online in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotCount.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotCount
eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotCount.description: This field indicates how many total snapshots are in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsVolumeNumInUse.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsVolumeNumInUse
eqlStoragePoolStatsVolumeNumInUse.description: This field indicates how many volumes are currently in use in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsVolumeNumOnline.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsVolumeNumOnline
eqlStoragePoolStatsVolumeNumOnline.description: This field indicates how many volumes are online in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsVolumeCount.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsVolumeCount
eqlStoragePoolStatsVolumeCount.description: This field indicates how many total volumes are in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsDelegatedSpace.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsDelegatedSpace
eqlStoragePoolStatsDelegatedSpace.description: This field indicates the total delegated space for partners in this pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsDelegatedSpaceUsed.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsDelegatedSpaceUsed
eqlStoragePoolStatsDelegatedSpaceUsed.description: This field indicates the total delegated space used by partners in this pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsMembersInUse.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsMembersInUse
eqlStoragePoolStatsMembersInUse.description: This field indicates the total members of online+offline members in this group. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsVolumeSubscribed.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsVolumeSubscribed
eqlStoragePoolStatsVolumeSubscribed.description: This field specifies the total subscribed space for all volumes in this pool. For a thin provisioned volume, subscribed space is the advertised space. For a regular volume, subscribed space is the volume size. The value of this field will be equal to sum of eqliscsiVolumeSize field for all volumes in this pool.

eqlStoragePoolStatsVolumeSpaceAllocated.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsVolumeSpaceAllocated
eqlStoragePoolStatsVolumeSpaceAllocated.description: The value of this object represents the sum of actual materialized pages for all volumes in the pool.

eqlStoragePoolStatsFailbackSpace.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsFailbackSpace
eqlStoragePoolStatsFailbackSpace.description: This field represents the amount of space consumed by fail-back replicasets in this pool.

eqlStoragePoolStatsThinProvFreeSpace.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsThinProvFreeSpace
eqlStoragePoolStatsThinProvFreeSpace.description: This field represents the amount of space available for Thin Provisioned Volumes in this pool.

eqlStoragePoolStatsConnectionCount.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsConnectionCount
eqlStoragePoolStatsConnectionCount.description: This field gives the number of iSCSI connections that are currently connected to volumes in this pool.

eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotResvFreeSpace.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotResvFreeSpace
eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotResvFreeSpace.description: This field specifies how many MB of space is available to Snapshots in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotResvBorrowing.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotResvBorrowing
eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapshotResvBorrowing.description: This field specifies the amount of free snapshot reserve that is being borrowed against by other volumes for either Recoverable Volumes or snapshots

eqlStoragePoolStatsFreeSpaceBorrowing.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsFreeSpaceBorrowing
eqlStoragePoolStatsFreeSpaceBorrowing.description: This field specifies the amount of free space that is being borrowed against by volumes for either Recoverable Volumes or snapshots

eqlStoragePoolStatsAvailableForBorrowing.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsAvailableForBorrowing
eqlStoragePoolStatsAvailableForBorrowing.description: This field specifies how many MB of space is still avaiable in this storage pool to borrow against.

eqlStoragePoolStatsRecoverableVolBorrowi.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsRecoverableVolBorrowing
eqlStoragePoolStatsRecoverableVolBorrowi.description: This field specifies the total amount of free space (in MB) that soft-deleted (i.e. recoverable) volumes are consuming in this pool. Recoverable volumes are permanently deleted by the array whenever the free space that they occupy is needed by the system.

eqlStoragePoolStatsActualFreeSpace.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsActualFreeSpace
eqlStoragePoolStatsActualFreeSpace.description: This field specifies the actual free space (in MB) that doesn't include soft-deleted (i.e. recoverable) volumes or borrowed space

eqlStoragePoolStatsTotalSpaceBorrowing.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsTotalSpaceBorrowing
eqlStoragePoolStatsTotalSpaceBorrowing.description: This field specifies the total space used for borrowing and includes Recoverable Volumes and Snapshots

eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapShotBorrowing.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapShotBorrowing
eqlStoragePoolStatsSnapShotBorrowing.description: This field specifies the total amount of borrowing for just snapshots

eqlStoragePoolStatsStorageContainerCount.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsStorageContainerCount
eqlStoragePoolStatsStorageContainerCount.description: This field specifies the total amount number of storage containers in the pool

eqlStoragePoolStatsStorageContainerSpace.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsStorageContainerSpaceReserved
eqlStoragePoolStatsStorageContainerSpace.description: This field specifies the total amount of pool space allocated to storage containers. The value is represented in MB. It is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsCompressedSpaceUsed.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsCompressedSpaceUsed
eqlStoragePoolStatsCompressedSpaceUsed.description: This field specifies how many MB of space is currently utilized for compressed pages in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value and cannot be set.

eqlStoragePoolStatsVirtualSpaceSize.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsVirtualSpaceSize
eqlStoragePoolStatsVirtualSpaceSize.description: This field specifies how many MB of space would be utilized by compressed pages in this pool if there was no compression.

eqlStoragePoolStatsStorageContainerVolum.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsStorageContainerVolumeCount
eqlStoragePoolStatsStorageContainerVolum.description: This field indicates the total volumes in storage containers within this this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsStorageContainerSnapC.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsStorageContainerSnapCount
eqlStoragePoolStatsStorageContainerSnapC.description: This field indicates the total snapshots in storage containers within this this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolStatsStorageContainerVolum.name: eqlStoragePoolStatsStorageContainerVolumesOnline
eqlStoragePoolStatsStorageContainerVolum.description: This field indicates the total online volumes in storage containers within this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountTable.name: eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountTable
eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountTable.description: EqualLogic-Persistent Admin Account Storage Pool Table. This table contains a list of privilege matchings of administrative accounts and the pools those administrators have access to.

eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountEntry.name: eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountEntry
eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountEntry.description: An entry (row) containing mapping of administrative accounts and their pool access.

eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountRowStatus.name: eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountRowStatus
eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountRowStatus.description: This field is used indicate the status of this entry.

eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountQuotaType.name: eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountQuotaType
eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountQuotaType.description: The format of the adminQuota value: 0 - Unlimited quota, 1 - Size in Megabytes. This field applies only to Volume Administrators.

eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountQuota.name: eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountQuota
eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountQuota.description: This field specifies the storage space quota (in MB) for a Volume Administrator in the storage pool. This field applies only to Volume Administrators.

eqlAdminAccountStoragePoolTable.name: eqlAdminAccountStoragePoolTable
eqlAdminAccountStoragePoolTable.description: EqualLogic-Dynamic table indicating the access an administrator has to a storage pool.

eqlAdminAccountStoragePoolEntry.name: eqlAdminAccountStoragePoolEntry
eqlAdminAccountStoragePoolEntry.description: An entry (row) containing the access privilege.

eqlAdminAccountStoragePoolAccess.name: eqlAdminAccountStoragePoolAccess
eqlAdminAccountStoragePoolAccess.description: The administrative permission to a storage pool.

eqlStoragePoolOpsEntry.name: eqlStoragePoolOpsEntry
eqlStoragePoolOpsEntry.description: An entry (row) containing storage pool configuration

eqlStoragePoolOpsIndex.name: eqlStoragePoolOpsIndex
eqlStoragePoolOpsIndex.description: This field unique identifies an operation withing a storage pool.

eqlStoragePoolOpsRowStatus.name: eqlStoragePoolOpsRowStatus
eqlStoragePoolOpsRowStatus.description: This field is used indicate the status of this entry.

eqlStoragePoolOpsOperation.name: eqlStoragePoolOpsOperation
eqlStoragePoolOpsOperation.description: The current operation for this drive group 0 - no operation 1 - delete/merge

eqlStoragePoolOpsStoragePoolDestinationI.name: eqlStoragePoolOpsStoragePoolDestinationIndex
eqlStoragePoolOpsStoragePoolDestinationI.description: This field unique identifies the destination Storage Pool.

eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountStatsTable.name: eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountStatsTable
eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountStatsTable.description: EqualLogic-Dynamic Storage Pool Admin Account Statistics Table. This table contains a list of pools in a group and their statistics.

eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountStatsEntry.name: eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountStatsEntry
eqlStoragePoolAdminAccountStatsEntry.description: An entry (row) containing storage pool admin account stats.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsQuota.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsQuota
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsQuota.description: This field specifies how many MB of quota comprises this storage pool for this account. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsQuotaUsed.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsQuotaUsed
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsQuotaUsed.description: This field specifies the number of MB used by volumes in this pool for this account. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsQuotaAvai.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsQuotaAvailable
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsQuotaAvai.description: This field specifies how many MB of space is available in this storage pool for this account. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotR.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotReserved
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotR.description: This field specifies how many MB of snapshot space is reserved in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotU.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotUsed
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotU.description: This field specifies how many MB of snapshot space is currently utilized in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotS.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotSubscribed
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotS.description: This field specifies the total subscribed space for all snapshots in this pool. For a snapshot of a thin provisioned volume, subscribed space is the advertised space. For a snapshot of a classic volume, subscribed space is the volume size. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotN.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotNumInUse
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotN.description: This field indicates how many snapshots are currently in use in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotN.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotNumOnline
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotN.description: This field indicates how many snapshots are online in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotC.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotCount
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotC.description: This field indicates how many total snapshots are in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeNum.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeNumInUse
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeNum.description: This field indicates how many volumes are currently in use in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeNum.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeNumOnline
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeNum.description: This field indicates how many volumes are online in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeCou.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeCount
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeCou.description: This field indicates how many total volumes are in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeSub.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeSubscribed
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeSub.description: This field specifies the total subscribed space for all volumes in this pool. For a thin provisioned volume, subscribed space is the advertised space. For a regular volume, subscribed space is the volume size. The value of this field will be equal to sum of eqliscsiVolumeSize field for all volumes in this pool.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeQuo.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeQuotaUsage
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeQuo.description: This field specifies the total MB against the quota for all volumes in this pool. The space contributed by a regular volume is its volume size. The sapce contributed by a thin provisioned volume is its max grow size.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeSpa.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeSpaceAllocated
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsVolumeSpa.description: The value of this object represents the sum of actual materialized pages for all volumes in the pool.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsFailbackS.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsFailbackSpace
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsFailbackS.description: This field represents the amount of space consumed by fail-back replicasets in this pool.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsFailbackS.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsFailbackSubscribed
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsFailbackS.description: This field specifies the total subscribed space for failback for all volumes in this pool. For the failback of a thin provisioned volume, subscribed space is the advertised space. For a failabck of a classic volume, subscribed space is the volume size. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsThinProvF.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsThinProvFreeSpace
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsThinProvF.description: This field represents the amount of space available for Thin Provisioned Volumes in this pool.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsConnectio.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsConnectionCount
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsConnectio.description: This field gives the number of iSCSI connections that are currently connected to volumes in this pool.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotR.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotResvFreeSpace
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSnapshotR.description: This field specifies how many MB of space is available to Snapshots in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSpaceUsed.name: eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSpaceUsed
eqlStorageAdminAccountPoolStatsSpaceUsed.description: This field specifies how many MB of space currently used by this account in this storage pool. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlLdapLoginAccessPoolTable.name: eqlLdapLoginAccessPoolTable
eqlLdapLoginAccessPoolTable.description: EqualLogic-Persistent Group LDAP login access group table. For LDAP login access configured with volume-admin this table stores the pool-quota information. For LDAP login access configured with pool-admin privilege this tables stores the pools that belong to the pool-admin

eqlLdapLoginAccessPoolEntry.name: eqlLdapLoginAccessPoolEntry
eqlLdapLoginAccessPoolEntry.description: An entry (row) containing the configuration for the LDAP login access pool information.

eqlLdapLoginAccessPoolQuotaType.name: eqlLdapLoginAccessPoolQuotaType
eqlLdapLoginAccessPoolQuotaType.description: The format of the adminQuota value: 0 - Unlimited quota, 1 - Size in Megabytes. This field applies only to the LDAP login access that have Volume Admin Privilege.

eqlLdapLoginAccessPoolQuota.name: eqlLdapLoginAccessPoolQuota
eqlLdapLoginAccessPoolQuota.description: This field specifies the pool quota (in MB) for a each Volume Administrator using the LDAP login access. This field applies only to Volume Administrators.

eqlLdapLoginAccessPoolQuotaRowStatus.name: eqlLdapLoginAccessPoolQuotaRowStatus
eqlLdapLoginAccessPoolQuotaRowStatus.description: This field is used indicate the status of this entry.

eqlStoragePoolOperStatusTable.name: eqlStoragePoolOperStatusTable
eqlStoragePoolOperStatusTable.description: EqualLogic-Dynamic Storage Pool Operational Status Table. This table contains the list of operational status for each pool.

eqlStoragePoolOperStatusEntry.name: eqlStoragePoolOperStatusEntry
eqlStoragePoolOperStatusEntry.description: An entry (row) containing a storage pool operational status.

eqlStoragePoolOperStatusCompression.name: eqlStoragePoolOperStatusCompression
eqlStoragePoolOperStatusCompression.description: This field the operational status of data optimization this pool.
